SHE SAID SORRY, BUT
THAT IS NOT ENOUGH.

36:17.827 --> 36:20.656
IT'S NOT ENOUGH.
SHE TOOK MY DAD
AWAY FROM ME.

36:20.700 --> 36:22.832
JACOB, YOUR DAD LOVES YOU.

36:22.876 --> 36:25.139
HE'S NOT MY DAD!

36:27.054 --> 36:30.449
A FAMILY IS SO MUCH
MORE THAN BLOOD, JACOB.

36:30.492 --> 36:32.581
IT'S SO MUCH MORE THAN DNA.

36:34.322 --> 36:36.237
YOU KNOW,
HE LOVES YOU SO MUCH

36:36.281 --> 36:40.198
THAT HE CONFESSED
TO BOTH MURDERS
TO PROTECT YOU.

36:43.462 --> 36:45.638
THAT'S ONLY
BECAUSE HE THINKS
THAT HE'S MY DAD.

36:45.681 --> 36:49.903
NO, JACOB, NO.
HE--HE KNOWS THE TRUTH.

36:49.946 --> 36:51.296
HE'S ALWAYS KNOWN.

36:51.339 --> 36:55.822
AND IT DIDN'T MATTER
TO HIM, IT DIDN'T.

36:55.865 --> 36:58.651
BECAUSE, JACOB,
HE LOVES YOU.

37:16.886 --> 37:18.105
OK. YOU OK?

37:18.148 --> 37:19.367
YEAH.

37:37.342 --> 37:39.648
ARE YOU SURE SHE
WANTS TO SEE ME?

37:39.692 --> 37:42.695
OH, YEAH, I'M SURE.

37:43.913 --> 37:45.872
ENTER AT YOUR OWN RISK.

37:53.009 --> 37:54.794
MY UNICORN MUG.

37:54.837 --> 37:56.578
I THREW THAT AWAY.

37:56.622 --> 37:59.059
I KNOW. I RESCUED IT.
I HOPE YOU DON'T MIND.

37:59.102 --> 38:00.800
NO, I DON'T MIND AT ALL.

38:00.843 --> 38:02.802
OH, GOOD, 'CAUSE
I COULDN'T HELP IT.

38:02.845 --> 38:05.935
I WANTED TO PUT IT
BACK TOGETHER FOR YOU.

38:05.979 --> 38:08.764
AND WHEN I WAS FIXING IT,
I REALIZED SOMETHING.

38:08.808 --> 38:11.027
YOU ARE NOT THE MUG.

38:11.071 --> 38:13.769
YOU'RE THE GLUE THAT HOLDS
THE MUG TOGETHER.

38:13.813 --> 38:16.381
COME ON.

38:16.424 --> 38:18.296
THANK YOU

38:18.339 --> 38:19.862
FOR LISTENING TO ME

38:19.906 --> 38:21.342
AND FOR UNDERSTANDING ME

38:21.386 --> 38:22.604
AND FOR BEING MY
MOST SPECIAL FRIEND

38:22.648 --> 38:24.302
AND MY BOSS
AT THE SAME TIME.

38:24.345 --> 38:27.566
OK. WELL, I HOPE YOU
STILL FEEL THAT WAY

38:27.609 --> 38:30.090
WHEN I TELL YOU THERE'S
SOMEONE HERE WHO WANTS
TO TALK TO YOU.

38:32.135 --> 38:34.399
DAVE AND I ASKED HIM TO COME.

38:37.053 --> 38:38.620
CARLOS.

38:38.664 --> 38:40.840
HEY, SIS.

38:43.495 --> 38:45.497
DID DAVID ROSSI
MAKE YOU COME HERE

38:45.540 --> 38:46.976
UNDER THREAT OF
BODILY HARM?

38:47.020 --> 38:48.500
NO, I'M HERE
'CAUSE I WANT TO BE.

38:48.543 --> 38:51.764
PRENTISS: I'M GONNA
LEAVE YOU TWO ALONE.

38:51.807 --> 38:54.157
I WANTED TO--YOU LOOK GOOD.

38:56.421 --> 38:57.900
LOOK, I KNOW
YOU'RE MAD AT ME

38:57.944 --> 38:59.902
ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED
AT THE PAROLE HEARING,

38:59.946 --> 39:02.383
AND I DON'T KNOW
HOW TO MAKE YOU
NOT BE MAD AT ME.

39:02.427 --> 39:04.690
LOOK, DO I UNDERSTAND
HOW YOU COULD FORGIVE

39:04.733 --> 39:06.953
THE MAN WHO MURDERED
OUR PARENTS? NO.

39:06.996 --> 39:10.130
I DON'T.

39:10.173 --> 39:12.306
I MIGHT NEVER UNDERSTAND.

39:14.917 --> 39:18.094
BUT I KNOW YOU,
AND I KNOW IT...

39:18.138 --> 39:20.836
CAME FROM A GOOD PLACE.

39:20.880 --> 39:22.925
THANK YOU.

39:22.969 --> 39:25.885
EMILY AND DAVE, THEY TOLD ME
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU.

39:27.060 --> 39:29.454
IT WAS BAD.I KNOW.

39:29.497 --> 39:31.020
I THOUGHT I WAS
GOING TO DIE.

39:33.109 --> 39:34.676
I'M SO SORRY.

39:34.720 --> 39:36.374
IT'S PART OF THE JOB.
IT'S OK.

39:36.417 --> 39:37.940
NO, IT'S NOT OK,

39:37.984 --> 39:39.812
'CAUSE I'M YOUR BROTHER.

39:41.248 --> 39:43.032
I'M SUPPOSED TO KNOW
WHEN YOU'RE IN TROUBLE.

39:54.217 --> 39:56.350
HEY.

39:58.874 --> 40:01.181
